                       Rewrite some code (optimizing).

    A_Sweeper V1.03ß : Fixed a bug which allowed to win quickly and easyly.
                       You just have to flag enough cells (the number of mines !).

    A_Sweeper V1.04ß : Aminet version.
                       Better look and documentation.

    A_Sweeper V1.05ß : Fixed a bug with gadget size in the settings window, after the first change. Changed the opening window (look and asynchrone loading). Saving Hi-scores added. Some code improvments. A big change : don't use the IFF brushes anymore, but icons instead, color remapping will look good this time, thanks to David McMinn.


@endnode


